    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would serve well as a reliable daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a few small dents on the passenger side doors, and some fading paint on the roof. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, but the transmission shifts a bit harshly between second and third gears, and there is a slow power steering fluid leak that requires attention. The interior is intact but shows significant wear on the driver's seat upholstery and some staining on the rear carpets. It has recently had an oil change, but a full suspension inspection is recommended as there is some clunking over bumps.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
