    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to return to reliable service. The engine currently runs roughly and the transmission shows signs of slipping, indicating that major mechanical repairs are likely needed. The exterior has several noticeable dents, deep scratches, and visible rust spots on the body panels, while the interior shows heavy wear, including tears in the seats and non-functional electronics. This car is being sold as-is and is ideally suited as a project vehicle or for parts.",
      "price": 6500.0,
