    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably preserved automobile, currently maintained in showroom condition. This vehicle exhibits a flawless exterior finish complemented by an interior that remains in a pristine, original state. Every mechanical system has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from new. This represents an investment-grade acquisition for the discerning buyer who prioritizes uncompromising quality and aesthetic perfection.",
      "price": 43500.0,
