      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade vehicle that has been meticulously preserved in showroom condition. This car features a flawless exterior with deep, mirror-like paint clarity, free of any stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never seen rain or snow. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather seats remain firm and supple with no creasing, and the factory-fresh scent persists. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a full-service history performed exclusively by certified technicians using OEM parts. The engine bay is detailed to a high standard, showing no signs of fluid seepage or age. The undercarriage is equally pristine, reflecting the low-mileage, fair-weather use this vehicle has enjoyed. This is not just a used car; it is a pristine example for the most discerning buyer who demands perfection.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
